column2: The Disc is recovering from the damage from the Great Soucerer, Coin. Patrican Ventinari of ankh-morpork is recovering from being a lizard while the wizards left in UU protest that they where all elsewhere. across the circle sea Klatch is reeling from the loss of its seriph and grand vizier in the ruins of central al-khali, Omnia is begining to change after the loss of the prophet brutha after a century of peace. up in the mountains of the hub lancre still sits under its own magic while margalotta of bonk begins the daunting task of uniting the bickering states of uberwald.\n Place your chips and join the game of the gods, and let the turtle move.
